title: Labs Extend Their Reign as Most Popular Dog
text: Let friends in your social network know what you are reading about Facebook Email Labs Extend Their Reign as Most Popular Dog Labrador retrievers have extended their record run as America's most popular dog breed, leading the American Kennel Club's rankings for a 26th straight year. Rottweilers are enjoying renewed favor as well, rising to America's 8th most popular dog breed.
